com.illposed.osc.OSCPacket

Packages that use OSCPacket
Package Description
com.illposed.osc
Provides the Java OSC API, which should be everything users of this library need.
com.illposed.osc.utility
Provides utility classes, used internally by the Java OSC API classes.

  • Uses of OSCPacket in com.illposed.osc

    Classes in com.illposed.osc that implement OSCPacket
    Modifier and Type Class Description
    class  OSCBundle
    A bundle represents a collection of OSC packets (either messages or other bundles) and has a time-tag which can be used by a scheduler to execute a bundle in the future, instead of immediately.
    class  OSCMessage
    An simple (non-bundle) OSC message.
